Package hms.common.id

Class IdRegistry

java.lang.Object
hms.common.id.IdRegistry
public class IdRegistry extends Object
Registry for managing IDs of classes. This class is used to manage the IDs of classes that need an ID. It provides methods to get the next ID suffix for a class, update the ID of a class, and try to update the ID of a class.
